":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"리미","body":"후후후, 엄청나게 좋아졌지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev210-ep1-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"타에","body":"나는 이 부분이 좋아.\n수많은 빛 가운데 내가 바라던 반짝임을 찾아낸 것 같아!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"ev210-ep1-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"사아야","body":"그렇지? 나도 그 부분에 신경을 썼어.\n왠지 앞으로 나아가고 싶은 가사야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"ev210-ep1-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":3}],"windowDisplayName":"리미","body":"모두의 말을 모아서 가사로 만들다니\n역시 카스미 짱이야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"ev210-ep1-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"카스미","body":"에헤헤~ 하지만 이